  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Is Based on Successive Approximation Register (SAR) principle"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Three clusters with different functionality are available"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "Primary converter cluster - Equipped with 8:1 multiplexers and 8-stage queues, conversion time down to below 0.5 μs",
        "Secondary converter cluster - Equipped with 16:1 multiplexers and 16-stage queues, conversion time down to below 1 μs",
        "Fast compare cluster - Single channels, update rate down to below 0.2 μs"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "TC37x has the below groups and channels for each clusters"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/EVADC%20-%20General%20Information/image2022-9-22_10-50-33.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/EVADC - General Information/image2022-9-22_10-50-33.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Most pins are connected redundantly to two group to achieve this functionality"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/EVADC%20-%20General%20Information/image2022-9-29_9-27-54.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/EVADC - General Information/image2022-9-29_9-27-54.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/EVADC%20-%20General%20Information/image2022-9-29_9-28-57.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/EVADC - General Information/image2022-9-29_9-28-57.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "panel_type": "info",
      "title": "",
      "content": "Fast Compare is not supported by MCAL ADC Driver"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/EVADC%20-%20General%20Information/image2022-9-22_10-51-42.png?api=v2",
